---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About" description="Learn about Quiet Atlas - an indie label creating healing-oriented, contemplative games.">
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="masthead">
        <div class="date">The Quiet Atlas Chronicle</div>
        <h1>About Us</h1>
        <p class="text-faded text-serif text-center">Volume I • The Beginning</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <article class="about-content container">
    <div class="content-width">
      <div class="article-lead fade-in">
        <p class="drop-cap">
          Quiet Atlas began with a simple belief: games can be medicine. Not in a clinical sense, 
          but in the way a long walk can be medicine, or the way sitting with an old friend in 
          comfortable silence can be medicine.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="pull-quote fade-in">
        "We make games for the moments when you need to feel held by something gentle."
      </div>

      <section class="about-section fade-in">
        <h2>What We Believe</h2>
        <p>
          We believe in games that don't demand. Games that invite. Spaces that feel more like 
          a hand on your shoulder than a challenge to overcome.
        </p>
        <p>
          This doesn't mean our games lack depth or meaning—quite the opposite. We believe 
          gentleness requires courage. Softness is a kind of strength.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="about-section fade-in">
        <h2>How We Create</h2>
        <div class="principles">
          <div class="principle">
            <h3>Low UI</h3>
            <p>Interfaces should whisper, not shout. We strip away everything that doesn't serve the feeling.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="principle">
            <h3>Low Friction</h3>
            <p>The path between wanting to play and actually playing should be as smooth as breathing.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="principle">
            <h3>High Atmosphere</h3>
            <p>Every pixel, every sound, every pause contributes to a world you want to inhabit.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="about-section fade-in">
        <h2>The Name</h2>
        <p>
          An atlas is a book of maps—a guide to worlds. We chose "Quiet" because our maps 
          lead to places of stillness. Places where the noise settles. Places where you can 
          hear yourself think, or better yet, stop thinking altogether.
        </p>
        <p>
          Quiet Atlas is a cartography of calm.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="about-section fade-in">
        <h2>Who We Are</h2>
        <p>
          Quiet Atlas is an indie label based in Ontario, Canada. We're small by design—big 
          enough to make things that matter, small enough to make them with care.
        </p>
        <p>
          Every game we release carries our belief that play can be a form of self-care. 
          That joy and tenderness aren't opposites. That wonder is ageless.
        </p>
      </section>

      <hr class="ornamental" />

      <div class="about-closing text-center fade-in">
        <p class="text-large text-serif">
          Thank you for being here.<br/>
          We hope our games find you when you need them.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    padding-top: var(--space-xl);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }
  
  .page-header h1 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }
  
  .about-content {
    padding-top: var(--space-xl);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
  }
  
  .article-lead {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }
  
  .article-lead p {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
  
  .about-section {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }
  
  .about-section h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ink-faded);
  }
  
  .about-section p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }
  
  /* Principles Grid */
  .principles {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    margin-top: var(--space-lg);
  }
  
  .principle {
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    border: 1px solid var(--ink-faded);
    background: var(--paper-aged);
    transition: all var(--duration-normal) var(--ease-gentle);
  }
  
  .principle:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(45, 41, 38, 0.08);
  }
  
  .principle h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    color: var(--accent);
  }
  
  .principle p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--ink-light);
    margin: 0;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .principles {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
  
  /* Closing */
  .about-closing {
    padding-top: var(--space-xl);
  }
  
  .about-closing p {
    max-width: 100%;
    color: var(--ink-light);
    line-height: 1.9;
  }
</style>
